要注意这方面的心理弱点，因为环境肯定是越来越差。学佛者都</description><dc:creator>Dao of Healing</dc:creator><media:content url="https://www.daoofhealing.org//img/%e6%89%93%e5%9d%90%e7%aa%8d%e8%af%802.assets/640-1671628409288-210.jpeg" medium="image"><media:title type="html">featured image</media:title></media:content><category>静坐</category><category>站桩</category><category>养生功法 Meditation &amp; Exercise</category><category>养生堂 Health Tutorials</category></item><item><title>关于打坐 | 不得不说的几个窍诀(一)</title><link>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/excercise/%E6%89%93%E5%9D%90%E7%AA%8D%E8%AF%801/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Nov 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Thu, 24 Nov 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/excercise/%E6%89%93%E5%9D%90%E7%AA%8D%E8%AF%801/</guid><description>气脉是否通畅 中国五千年文化有很多非常了不起的传承，比如说道家、佛家的等等。我们发现，从古至今得到一些成就的人基本上是通过打坐获得的。比如王阳</description><dc:creator>Dao of Healing</dc:creator><media:content url="https://www.daoofhealing.org//img/%e6%89%93%e5%9d%90%e7%aa%8d%e8%af%801.assets/640-1671630296005-237.jpeg" medium="image"><media:title type="html">featured image</media:title></media:content><category>静坐</category><category>站桩</category><category>养生功法 Meditation &amp; Exercise</category><category>养生堂 Health Tutorials</category></item><item><title>[置顶]站桩与静坐详细教程</title><link>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/excercise/meditation-detailed-guide/</link><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 21 Jun 2020 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/excercise/meditation-detailed-guide/</guid><description>姿势与要领 那么站桩和静坐，首先来讲它们的原理其实是一样的，只不过我们把它区分了。 从相上来讲，一个是站着，一个是坐着。现在来讲的话，我们很多人</description><dc:creator>Dao of Healing</dc:creator><media:content url="https://www.daoofhealing.org//img/meditation-detailed-guide.assets/9109a2_7a6f160881b244028452d0f0a2b2c727mv2.webp" medium="image"><media:title type="html">featured image</media:title></media:content><category>静坐</category><category>站桩</category><category>养生功法 Medit